{"tid":672713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[Double]東涌及屯門兩男墮樓亡！","createTime":"2018-05-21T08:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T08:35:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac061511f156ba8d4dcfd6056f4dd9f7d43eb24","tid":672713,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"東涌及屯門發生墮樓案！上午約9時，逸東邨康逸樓，一名69歲男子由高處墮下。救護員接報到場，證實男子當場死亡，警召仵工到場將遺體移送殮房。警方正展開調查，據了解死者有身體病紀錄，警員於現場沒有檢獲遺書。<br />\n另一宗墮樓發生在上午11時許，現場為屯門屯喜路2號，一名男子由高處墮下，跌在正門附近。救護員接報到場，證實男子明顯死亡。警方正調查其身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/190607/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E4%BB%B5%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%87%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E9%80%81%E6%AE%AE%E6%88%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F190607%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E4%25BB%25B5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2581%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%25AE%25AE%25E6%2588%25BF&d=DoICCXueYBTyWI%2Bktal2rp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1b35148f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/190607/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E4%BB%B5%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%87%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E9%80%81%E6%AE%AE%E6%88%BF</a>"},{"pid":"4ad86d04487df26faf2e05ac6a2ab8e4a0436e31","tid":672713,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"may be 700 drop too much<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}